    <summary>Fast Vim-inspired TUI hex editor</summary>
    <description># dz6

Fast Vim-inspired TUI hex editor

## Features

- Fast, even when editing large files
- Runs in the terminal / Text User Interface (TUI)
- Vim-like key bindings
- Configurable options
- Edit in hex or ASCII
- String list with regex filtering
- Multiple smart ways to navigate through a file
- Find strings and hex bytes
- Cross-platform
- Open source

![Screenshot](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/dz6/img/screenshot.png)

</description>
